<paragraph pageId="0" pageNumber="577">Type locality.</paragraph>
<paragraph pageId="0" pageNumber="577">
Mudumallay, near Wayanad [i.e., Mudumalai hills, in Nilgiris dt., Tamil Nadu, India] in the Western Ghats (
